    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-06-04T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-06-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="36"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d36">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Moonlight</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-06-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 4, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 12.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have received your No. 8, of the 5th ultimo,
                    inclosing a copy of your note to the Bolivian minister of foreign affairs
                    recommending the promotion of Maj. Romulo Fortún, of the Bolivian army, in
                    recognition of courtesies and kindnesses received from him during your
                    reception. You state that you were assured that this was expected, and according
                    to custom.</p>
                <p>However usual such a proceeding may be in Bolivia, it is so entirely contrary to
                    section 1751 of the Revised Statutes that the Department can not approve your
                    note, and you should make a proper explanation to the minister of foreign
                    affairs.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">W. Q. Gresham.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
